Ɓumɓɛ a Egiɓtɛn ɓɛ resa ̀ ka ̀ Moyis ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kaa ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ki mum lɛ , ri ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii , ri ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mii .
N ̀ ti n ̀ fafa ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll wɛ ̀ m ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m , n ̀ ki yiiyiti ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yɛm ̀ ,
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi maa ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ a ̀ dɛŋ , nni ɓɛ ̀ kukwiy ntɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛ yugha ̀ nyi ki ̀ ɓoŋi ̀ , ɓɛ rɛli ̀ i ̀ fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ , ɓɛ kpaa jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ :
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : I ɓya ̀ a ri ̀ ri ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ , di ɓi ̀ yin ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓa ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓe ; nni yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi kpaakpaa lɛ ɓi ghɛɛghɛnɛ ̀ n , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ki ̀ ɓe kin ki kaka .
Nni ɓɛ ɓaka ̀ nyi lɛ : Ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaaghi lɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ Zyaŋ Ba ̀ ɓtis , ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog lɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ Eli , ɓɛmbog ti ̀ lɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Yeesus a ̀ kali ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɛm ̀ ki ka kpaŋ ɓi , mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ bogtɛ ̀ n , mum a ̀ ki ɓa girig bog ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ ri ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɓum , nnyɛɛ ri Yeesus Kiris a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mum ;
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓis ɓɛ ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem wu ya ̀ aka ri Yoosɛɓ a ̀ geni wa ̀ a ̀ , nni ɓɛ ka ̀ ɓka ̀ nyi a Egiɓtɛn .
I mum ɓi mi ̀ ni a ̀ tanɛɛ ri ̀ n ̀ tɔɓ , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzii Bɛ ̀ ll , nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓɔgsii Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ tyem .
Nni ɓɛ woka ̀ bim yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ tanɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ -Pyɛɛri ɓɛɛ ̀ re ̀ resi ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ ɓuŋɓu ̀ ŋ ki ̀ ɓan ki ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi Yeesus , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓiloŋ .
Ki ̀ gwey ki ɓum ki ri ɓɔ ɓii ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ tii ɓi ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g kaa ki cɛɓ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ feefengi ̀ bee i ̀ saaɗ lɛ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗyaa .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ nga ̀ ŋwosi ̀ sɔnɗi ̀ sariwa , a ̀ loka ̀ ki ̀ re ̀ sɛɛ Marii Madelɛn . Marii a ̀ nɛ ̀ n nnɛ Yeesus a ̀ pisi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi nyoo .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , n ̀ tɔɔgh mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi niɗ mɛ ̀ rem , ɓi ̀ teɗ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓyɛɛ fa mi ̀ ni i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓi mɛ ̀ rem ɓisuulɛ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ n ̀ ka ̀ nii ̀ mi ̀ ni a ̀ ra ̀ ɓi ɓi .
Ki ̀ say kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki nki ̀ ki ̀ , n ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ ri ̀ nghɛɓsɛn wu i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wii wu wɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki kisay ɓi mɛ ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpaga ̀ be ̀ g mɛ ̀ tin mɛɓɛɛ ̀ lɛ rinɗim , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓeka ̀ lɛ a kɛn ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛ Isirayɛl ɓɛ ɓɛgeni ɓii .
Ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey ɓɛ renga ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ wey girig Lazaari .
Yeesus a ̀ kaka a ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni coo kituu ki ɓum ki yugha ̀ y , ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ntɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ɗii lɛ Zyudas kɛɛ syoga ̀ y bee . A ̀ tyo ̀ ŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ Yeesus a nyoo lɛ a lɔɛɗ nyi .
Mɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaa ɓɛ ̀ kwɛ ̀ y ri ̀ mɛ ̀ kpɔɓ mɛ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ lɛ , ki ri ki ̀ rɔɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ kɔri fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n i ̀ pani ̀ gha ̀ , nni a ̀ ɗiŋigha ̀ ɓi naa , a ̀ ɓan mutya ̀ a ̀ giɓ anɛ a ̀ wugha ̀ a ̀ nɛn ɓi ca ̀ g ; mutya ̀ a ̀ giɓ a pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n aɗyoo .
