I Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ wɔ ̀ di u ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kpa ̀ n , n ̀ ɗem wɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ cɛɛcɛɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n wɔ ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ɗi ̀ n , wɔ ̀ lɛ i u ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ bee inɛ lɛ u pɛsɛn ɓi ri ̀ kpa ̀ n , u ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n , kɔ ̀ ɔ ki ̀ wa ̀ ŋ .
Nyii teka ̀ ɓi ga ̀ ɓ ɓi ri ̀ ren ɗi ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ renga ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ wey Yeesus , nsoo ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ ɓɛ kiki ̀ gha ̀ nyi . Yoosɛɓ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ lɛ Arimate , a ̀ ki ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋga ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓa ̀ agh gɛ girig nyi lɛ : Kan , fin innɛ ti ̀ ghɛnga ̀ wɔ ̀ di za ̀ y yɛ ̀ ɛ kɔ ̀ nkɔn wɔ , nsoo ̀ lɛ di ki ̀ nɔli kɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki wɔ , nsoo ̀ lɛ di u ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ke ̀ n , nsoo ̀ lɛ nyoozɛy , nsoo ̀ lɛ roro ̀ ɓ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y , ti ̀ ki rɔ ̀ ɓ tyɛ ̀ ki ghɛɓsi wɔ ?
