Fɔɔnnɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ fiɓi ̀ gha ̀ n ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh win ̀ wɔɔ ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : I ti ̀ ɓa ̀ agh nyi lɛ ba ̀ ɓtis i ̀ Zyaŋ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ y yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ si ɓii ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh lɛ , nni ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi yɔ ̀ ?
Ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi lɛ ɓɛ wɔɔsi ̀ nyi ɓi ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓii ɓi a ̀ to ̀ to ̀ ka ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ ; wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɗi a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ , ɓɛ mam .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ mancɛɛ Pol a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ woka ̀ dwi ̀ ɗ inɛ ̀ n , nni a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ lɔka ̀ Pol , a ̀ wogsi ̀ nyi yɔ ̀ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi tuu ̀ tuu anɛ ɓɛ nɗegi ̀ lɛ , tuu ̀ tuu a Salomɔŋ .
Ri ̀ yi ɗi ti ̀ yii com ki lɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi lɛ , Yeesus Kiris a ̀ fagha ̀ cɛɓ kii ɓisu wis ; fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ si girig , ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ faa ̀ cɛɓ kis ɓisuu ɓɛgeni ɓis .
a ̀ kpaa mɛ ̀ lɛ : Pol , kɔ ̀ ɔ risi , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ , u kpaa ̀ sɛn ɓi mis mɛ Kaaza , wɔ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ka ̀ mɛɛ ri ɓyɛɓ ɓi ɓumɓɛ ɓi kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛɛ ri ɓɔ ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ ɓisu wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Lɛ u ̀ ɓe ̀ ga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɛ ̀ m ɗi ̀ ki ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ mɛ ̀ girig n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn mɛ mɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ yu ̀ u ɓi ziinɛ bimiɗ lɛ mɛɛ fee ̀ ghrɛn ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi ziinɛ .
Fɔɔnnɛ roa ̀ ntonto a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ y a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , fi ̀ raŋ ̀ fyɔɔ fi gol fi n-yali tidɛŋ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ .
Nni ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ cɛcɛɗ ki riɓa ̀ y ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ɓɛ-Gerazenyɛŋ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog mum bimiɗ a ̀ ti a ̀ ɓala ̀ g ri ̀ mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓiɓan ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔn nyi ɓyɛɛ ti ɓi syogi ̀ nyi , ɓi ki teki nyi nɗem .
Nni ɓɔɔ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ tɔka ̀ lɛ : Yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll wa ? Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi ̀ kpaa mii ̀ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓɛ yu Yeesus a nyoo , ɓɛ ghɛn ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay lɛɛ ̀ gwey n ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔriyɛn , nni i ̀ ris wu ɓanga ̀ ɓɔ .
Yeesus a ̀ ba ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni saaɗ lɛ , i ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ɓi ̀ ki ɓa kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ nyoey ɓi nɗem , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki n ̀ ki ̀ i fi ̀ gyee a ̀ nɛ ki , ɓi ̀ ki ɓa ti kɔm ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , i ɓi ̀ kpaa do ̀ n i ̀ nɛ lɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ pɛsɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kpi ̀ i ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y , ki kilɛ ̀ n fɔlɔɔ .
Ti ɓɔ ̀ ɔɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ i ̀ ru yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwos , ti ̀ ki si ̀ i ̀ rɛn ɓi bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n lɛ a ki lɛ ti ghɛnag ti ̀ a mɛ ̀ su , a ̀ ki roozi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi kaarɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin ?
Ɓi ɗi lɛ tyɛ ̀ ki ɓiisɛn wɔ ki ̀ yeesii , m ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzii wɔ ̀ lɛ , u ram ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ̀ , u wog ki ̀ ɓan ki nki ̀ ki lɛ n ̀ ɗesi wɔ ̀ ki ̀ den lɛ cɔs .
