Nni masa ̀ wi ̀ i ̀ a woka ̀ bim , a ̀ kpaa ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓan ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say anɛ ̀ n , ɓɛɛ foŋ nyi ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y , a ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ le ̀ gsii ki pee ̀ pon wii ̀ .
N ̀ ɗere ̀ ŋi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ri ̀ Gi ̀ rɛg lɛ ɓɛɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛ ̀ rem , ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ n Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ ki tyweeyi Yeesus a ̀ Kan wi ̀ s .
Ɓi ̀ yii ɓi lɔŋ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓiɓan , ɓaa ɓa ɓi ri i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll ? Kɛ ̀ ɓi pwa ̀ a ̀ rɛn , a ̀ tumɛɛ lɛ , ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ghɛghɛɓ cɛɓ ki tifin , a ̀ kpaŋ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g ,
Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛ ɓii ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ fyo ̀ oma ̀ fi ri lɛ fyo ̀ oog kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki risiyɛn kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓɛ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ si ̀ gmɛɛ lɛ cuu ki mɛ sɛn ɓi ɓɔ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ kɛŋ ɗi riyay ɗi ti ɗi siɗki ̀ giɓ a ɗyem . Ɓaa ɓa ɓi ri bee i ̀ n ̀ lɛghɛn cuu ki ̀ n .
I ŋwaa ̀ tɔɔgh mi ̀ ni com , ɓi ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Kan yɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ngi lɛ ti kɛn ̀ nyi ri ̀ yɔ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ ca ̀ ri lɛ , ɓi yuiy ri ̀ yɔ .
Ɓɔn ɓɛm , n ̀ ka ̀ ni mi ̀ ni ki ̀ ɓan ki lɛ , di kɛ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ kiɓe ; wɔ ̀ lɛ i ki kpaŋi lɛ wa ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ u ̀ ki ̀ i ki ̀ ɓe , ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a kamɛn ɗi ̀ ɓi ̀ si ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , nnyɛɛ ri Yeesus Kiris a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ saaɗ a ̀ mum .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi rom yi wɔ ̀ Aritemas nsoo ̀ lɛ Tisig , u ̀ fyaŋzi ̀ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ yu ̀ u ki tanɛɛ a Nikopolis lɛ wɔɔ nnɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nkpaa lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ghagsii bu ̀ ma ̀ .
Nni ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ Yeesus lɛ Zyudas Iskariyot a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ki ̀ ka ̀ ɓi , a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɛ :
Nni Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ̀ n , a ̀ na ̀ ri ̀ be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y a ̀ nɛ a Galile , a ̀ ɓɔg ɓi do ̀ n aɗyoo , a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓi zi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Bɛtilɛhɛm ɓi zii ̀ Zyude , ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki Eroodɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m , nni ɓɛ ̀ yii ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ Pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ɓi ja ̀ ŋ i ̀ nɛ ŋ ̀ wos a kpagii , ɓɛ yuiy a Yorisalɛm
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓi be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y , coo kituu ki ɓum ki nɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ nyi ; ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a Galile ri ̀ a Zyude
Ŋwaa ̀ fi ̀ tom a Kan a ̀ kpaagha ̀ Filiɓ lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo , u nɔɔ ̀ ti bee inɛ i ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ a Yorisalɛm i ̀ sɛn a Gaza , ɓum ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ fyee ti ɓi bee ince ̀ m .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓeŋɓe ̀ ŋga ̀ Yeesus ɓɛ fee ̀ fe ̀ nga ̀ ka ̀ nyi di ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓooɓoki ̀ nyi .
Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ yin lɛ ɓɛ wog ri ̀ kpaa ɗin ̀ , i ki cee ɓi lɛ , ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ki ri ki ̀ fayɛn lɛ ɓɛɛ wog ɗyɔ .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis ɓi nfala ̀ g i ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ wu n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey , ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɔŋ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ ki ki ̀ ɓe ; wɔ ̀ lɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ɓi bɛ ̀ ɗ inɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis , i ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ gha ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti ɓi nɗɛli wulɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ na ̀ a ̀ di isuu ̀ ce ̀ m .
Fɔɔnnɛ ri ̀ kem ɗi Yeesus ɗi ghaska ̀ ki sa ̀ a ɓi zii ̀ Galile bimiɗ .
Mi ̀ ni ɓumɓɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ : mi ̀ ni lɛ du ̀ ŋdu ̀ ŋ , ɓi ̀ ki ɓa ti ri ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ , ri ̀ gol ri ̀ naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ lɛ gol yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓa ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ , cɛ kɛɛ cee kimbog ?
Ɓi ɓɛg wi ̀ s , ti ̀ keesii Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ , nyimiɗ yɛɛ loka ̀ ɓi ̀ si ki ̀ keesii .
a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ti ti ̀ i n ̀ ɗɔ ̀ gsɛɛ mi ̀ ni syeesyee a ̀ ri ̀ rɔ ̀ gsɛ ̀ n lɛ , kɛ ̀ ɓi re ̀ si ti mum ɗii di ̀ n ? Nni ghɛɛna com ki ɓi ̀ ki ̀ i , ɓi ̀ sa ̀ a ̀ tii ri ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗin ̀ ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ Yorisalɛm bimiɗ , ɓi ki ̀ kɔ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ di ɓya ̀ a saghii ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ wu ɗi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓi n ̀ to .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛmbog ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ki kɛŋ ɓɔ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kpaa ̀ masa ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ , com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ki ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ teka ̀ nya Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ? Ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓaa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Ɓi ̀ sii ka woka ̀ ɓi ̀ gi di ɓɛ ɓuŋi com kidɛŋ lɛ Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay .
A ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa , kɛ ̀ ɛ ghɛnɛn , kɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi , kɛ ̀ ɛ nɔ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ nsoo ̀ bwaɓ yɛm ̀ yaa ki kpaŋi ̀ ɓi si ̀ g a ̀ com ki ɓɛ funɛɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , lɛ yɛɛ ɓɔɓtɛn ɓi ri ̀ fa ɗi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ɗyɔ , fɔlɔɔ a fa lɔŋ mɛ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ , n ̀ ki nya ̀ a ̀ rɛn n ̀ ɗaŋ ri mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ ɓyom yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ ro ̀ o ̀ mɛ ɗuu , ɓince ̀ m ɓi ̀ ghasakɛn dɛŋ-dɛ ̀ ŋ-dɛŋ di ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɓɛli ɓɔ ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
ki ̀ ɓan kifog mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ ɓi ziinɛ , ri ̀ ki ̀ see ki ikum , ri ̀ gɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ambog a ̀ nɛ a syo ̀ ŋsyoŋ mɛrem , ɓi laata ̀ g jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛn yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛn bee inɛ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ wum ɓi ̀ du ̀ n .
I ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓeni ki ̀ gherɛɛ lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ n ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Yeesus , nsoo ̀ mi ̀ ni , mi ̀ nii ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ gherɛɛ lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ n ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , ɓisuulɛ mi ̀ ni yɛɛ ri ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ki ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ɗi n ̀ ɗi ̀ n ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , ɓi cɛɓ ki ɓi ghɛghɛɓ ɓi Kan ɓi ɗu ̀ m .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ kpaga ̀ a Yorisalɛm , nni Yeesus a ̀ ɗini ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ na ̀ ɓ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kaka ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓyom ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ lala ̀ ka ̀ ; fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ɓigta ̀ ka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ teɓe ̀ re ̀ ɓɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ cee ̀ ce ̀ nɗi ̀ gha ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni , a ̀ ɓigta ̀ g girig mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛ ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛ kaka ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kuu ̀ kuu ̀ .
Nni kwiy a ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghaska ̀ ki ̀ ku ̀ rɛɛ , nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ i sugti ̀ lɛ syeesyee .
Ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka kpaagha ̀ ɓi ŋwaa ̀ fi ̀ tom adɛŋ lɛ : U ̀ ri ̀ Man wɛm ̀ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , n ̀ ti soŋi ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ Seŋi , nyii ɓa mɛ ̀ Man .
