A ̀ kpaŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u , si ̀ i ̀ rɛn ɓi ri ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓa ̀ y ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ ri ̀ rere ̀ ɓ ɗi ɓum , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ re ̀ e ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi ɓɔ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓi lɛ , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ sɛkɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ kin ̀ lɛsaaɗ yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus lɛ gu ̀ l i ̀ gheka ̀ bee ; nni ɓɛ pini ̀ gha ̀ fi ̀ ran ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ Yeesus a ̀ rɛrɛ ̀ li ̀ gha ̀ , ɓɛ rɔŋzi ̀ i ̀ min ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n fɔlɔɔ ɓi kon wii ̀ .
