Ɓi duri tana , za ̀ y i ̀ kɔ ̀ nga ̀ Yeesus di ɓɛ mɛ pɛ ̀ sɛn yi a Bɛtanii .
Re ̀ siina mɛ ̀ wog ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ki ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓum ɓɛ foŋi ɓisuu Kan , nsoo ̀ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗyɛ yaa ri ̀ , ɓi ̀ ki ̀ ɗyɔ mɛ ̀ wog lɛ ɗi ri n ̀ la ̀ mi a ̀ gwey ,
Ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓsɛ ̀ nga ̀ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n yi ̀ ɓi Samuɛl , ɓɛ ɓuga ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ min ɓi nyimiɗ , a ̀ kpaa lɛ , n ̀ konaagh min ki ghɛɛ ̀ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ lɛ , Kan a ̀ a romii ̀ mum wii ̀ a ̀ fi ̀ tom , a ̀ sɔri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓi Eroodɛ , a ̀ ki lɛgsi mɛ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m mɛ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ n ̀ fe ̀ feegh lɛ n ̀ ghɛn .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ : Wɔ ̀ ki ̀ ye ̀ g ki mum ki , lɔŋ ɓi-ru wu gɛɛ ̀ nɛ nnɛ ɓɛ ri wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓa ̀ tɛɛ cɛɓ kɔɔ ; nni gɛ com a ̀ nɛ u ̀ mɛ nyam anɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓii ̀ wooghrɛɛ ri ghɛn ?
Eli a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɔŋ mum fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ si , nni a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ ka ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ nɗem wii wuce ̀ m lɛ bwey yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ nɔ , fɔɔnnɛ be ̀ g yi ghaghi ̀ gha ̀ yiraa ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii taa ̀ fog , bwey yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ nɔ ɓi ziinɛ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Zakarii a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ nyi , a ̀ ɓuu ̀ sɛ ̀ n , iris wu ɓan nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nnɛ a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n lɛ : Mi ̀ ni ɓumɓɛ a Isirayɛl , ɓi cɛ nnɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri mɛ ̀ kuu ̀ kuugh ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ? Ɓisuucɛ nnɛ ɓi fifiɓi ɓisi lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kali lɛ ti ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sii ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wis , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ falɛ ̀ n ɗis ɗi ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ?
Nni Sata ̀ n a teka ̀ nyi , a ̀ ɓɔgtɛ ̀ n ti ̀ ri ̀ nyi aɗyoo , a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ nyi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi ziinɛ , ɓi maa ki ̀ den a ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ,
Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ a kɛ ̀ ɓtɛn ɓi fiɓa ̀ g ɓisu wɛ ̀ m .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ nɗɛlii ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m , ɓum ɓɛ kiɓan ɓɛ n ̀ kpaa ɓi nsoo ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓeɓtɛn ɓi mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ fe ̀ feegh lɛ , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ a ̀ ki ̀ .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ a saa ̀ sa ̀ nɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ saasanɛ ̀ n ɓi Kan ɓiɗu ̀ m .
Ɓisuulɛ Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ ɓɛɛ ̀ si ̀ i ̀ rag ɓi n ̀ dɛli wulɛ : Com kidɛŋ ki yin lɛ ri ̀ ghe ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓilo ̀ ŋ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛ titom , nsoo ̀ lɛ n ̀ ghay . Wɔ ̀ lɛ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɔɔ ̀ ghera ̀ g lɛ ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ri wɔɔ .
Ɓisuulɛ n ̀ la ̀ nag wu yin yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a ki ̀ raa a ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ y di a kpaakpaa jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : I mum a ̀ ɓɔgsii nya ̀ m ri ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki yɔ ̀ nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓɛ teɗ nyi ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ki nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛn ɓisu nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓi ca ̀ g ,
I mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓtɛɛ mɛ ̀ rem ɓɛ , ɓi ̀ yii ri ̀ fa ɗi ɓɔn ɓin ɓyom ɓi syeesyee , lannɛ Seŋi wi ̀ n anɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m yɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓi kɛ ̀ ɛ fa ɓyom ɓi syeesyee a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ lɔni nyi ɓyɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pilat a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ kaka ɓi naa ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m , nni gil a romga ̀ y mum lɛ a kpaa nyi lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ gha ̀ ɓ gaa i ̀ nɛ ɓi saaɗ a ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , lɛ ɓi-ru wu gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm ɓyaa yeesii mɛ ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓisu wi ̀ i ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ ko ̀ m mɛ , ɓisuulɛ n ̀ ka ɓɔg ɓi yɛ ̀ ɛ Seŋi wɛ ̀ m ; ki ̀ ɓan kifog kɛ ̀ na a ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ̀ m , u kpaa ɓɔ lɛ m ̀ ɓɔɔgh yɛ ̀ ɛ Seŋi wɛ ̀ m , nnyɛɛ ri girig Seŋi wi ̀ n , yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll wɛ ̀ m , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ girig Bɛ ̀ ll wi ̀ n .
Nni ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛmbog ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : Tya ̀ a ghɛɛ Kan . Tomas a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : I n ̀ ghɛɛ ɓi ɓifi ̀ li ̀ ɓi tyɛmi ̀ ɓi ɓya ̀ g ɓii , kɛ ̀ ɛ nki foŋ mana ̀ ca ̀ g wɛm ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ fi ̀ li ̀ ɓi tyɛmi ̀ nsoo ̀ lɛ n ̀ foŋ ca ̀ g kɛm ̀ ɓi be ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ , n ̀ -yin lɛ n ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
Kɔ ̀ ɔ risi ntɔɓ wu u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ tulɛɛ ri wɔ . Ghɛna lɛ Sata ̀ n a ri ̀ ɓii ̀ pi ̀ igh kigwey ki ɓi mi ̀ ni ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y lɛ a fee ̀ ghrɛn mi ̀ ni , fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ tulɛɛ ri n ̀ -yeesɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ finɛɛ mɛru n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ . Si ̀ i ̀ rɛn ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaŋ a ri ̀ wu , fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ ta ̀ m a ̀ cɛɓ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ fee ̀ fe ̀ ngi ̀ com ki ɓɛ yii ɓi , ki ɓɔɔ ̀ fe ̀ ki lɛ ɓɛ yii , ɓi fe ̀ g wa ̀ a ̀ anɛ a ̀ ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ fe ̀ g a ̀ nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n , kɛɛ ki ti , ki piki ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ri ̀ ɗyaŋ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ gi ̀ ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ :
Nni Levi a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ ca ̀ ɗ ɓyom ɓii ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ nyi .
Ɓisuulɛ a ̀ rɛsi ̀ gha ̀ bimiɗ a ̀ ŋwos a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ yɔ ̀ mi zi bimiɗ mii ̀ , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ saaɗ a kɔ ̀ nkɔ ̀ n ; a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nga ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i kisay kin ̀ , a ̀ fa ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ki ki resii lɛ , nnyɛɛ ɓɔnga ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nce ̀ m , yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ghe ̀ mzi ̀ gha ̀ y nyi a ɓi ̀ loŋ .
Ɓɔɔ ɓaa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Moyis a ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ baŋi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ falag giy kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ lɛ a ghasɛɛ ri ̀ nyi , fɔɔnnɛ i ̀ ki na ̀ ɓ min nyi .
Lɛ ri ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗi ɓiɓan ɓi ɓi seesee cɛɓ ki Kiris ɗi mɛ ɓag ga ̀ ŋ ri i ̀ te ̀ ɗ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin .
Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ tɔg nyi lɛ : Raɓi ̀ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɛlɛ ri ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ lɛ nyimiɗ yɛɛ kigha ̀ ki ̀ ɓe gi ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓii ?
Cɛ kɛɛ ri lɛ ki ki lɛ ri ̀ Kiris ri ̀ Sata ̀ n ɓɛɛ kpaŋ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bog ? Nsoo ̀ lɛ ɓas aɗi yɛɛ ri lɛ a ̀ ɓa lɛ ri ̀ n ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin ngherɛ ̀ n ?
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɔm ̀ kin ̀ , nnɛ , m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -naa ̀ -za ̀ y a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ lɛ a soo ̀ ɓɔ beŋ yi ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ yɔ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓtii lɛ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓum ɓii ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓyɛm ̀ a ̀ ki ɓe ̀ ŋ ɓyɔ , nnyɛɛ keesii mɛ ̀ . Nni ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ keesii mɛ ̀ innɛ Seŋi wɛ ̀ m a ̀ ɓii ̀ kesii , mɛ ̀ n ̀ keesi ̀ girig nyi , n ̀ ki re ̀ sɛn nyi lɛ a yi mɛ ̀ .
Nni mɛ ̀ n ̀ kalii wɔ ̀ lɛ , u ̀ ri ̀ gɔ ̀ g , nni mɛ ̀ m ̀ ɓii ̀ toŋi ̀ ki ̀ seŋi kɛ ̀ m ɓi gɔ ̀ g i ̀ nɛ ̀ n aɗyo ̀ o ̀ . Fɔɔnnɛ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu riwu ̀ waa ɓa ɓi ri bee i ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ yɛn com ɗi ̀ ki ̀ seŋi ki ̀ n .
Ɓi woka ̀ lɛ ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Keesi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ wubsɛɛ wɔ ̀ , u ̀ ɓe ̀ e ̀ zɛ ̀ n be ̀ na ̀ bena wɔɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ sii lolo ̀ ka ̀ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ fi fi kɛnkɛ ̀ nga ̀ a Asɔs , wɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ teetii Pol , ɓisuulɛ nyii kɔnkɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ , a kpaŋ wɔɔ ɓi zi .
Ɓɛ ɓomga ̀ mi ̀ ni n ̀ ɗaŋ ri nyi yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓtɛ ̀ nga ̀ , ɓi ̀ mɛ ghe ̀ mɓɛn girig ɓi nyi , n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi nyi lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓi ̀ gherɛɛ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghe ̀ mzi ̀ gha ̀ y nyi a ɓi ̀ loŋ .
Pɛ ̀ sɛɛna aɗyoo , ti kɛn ̀ lɛ , roa ̀ nɛ a ka ̀ kaɓ mɛ a ̀ tii ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ ɗigha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g , i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu yuti ̀ nyi ɓi nyoo . A ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ a Damas .
ɓi ̀ re ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɓɔ ɓɔlɛ a ̀ cɛɓ ; ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ri mɛ ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki nkeŋkem mii ̀ ɓi ŋwos a Kiris , ki ki re ̀ si lɛ n ̀ kpuu ̀ kpu ̀ tɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi , kɛ ̀ ɛ nki ɗiɗig mɛtɔɓ zɛy .
Ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɛ , ɓɛ loka ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ Tirofim a ̀ nɛ a Efɛɛzɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ Pol ɓi ba ̀ n , ɓɛ feki ̀ nya lɛ Pol a ̀ a ɗiŋzii nyi ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll .
Mɛ ̀ ɛ m ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɔɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ naɓ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki n ̀ ghay ki ̀ n , nni ki n-yaagh ɓɔ ri ̀ na ̀ ɓ .
Ti tyo ̀ ŋdɛɛna min Bɛ ̀ ll ja ̀ ŋbog ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem wu wu ri lɛ sɛɛghi sɛɛghi , ri ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ɗi ri ɗi ̀ ronɛn , n ̀ ɗem wu ̀ tɛnɛn ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri lɛ ɓi fa wɔ ̀ bɛ ̀ lɛn , nyoo i ̀ ɓa n ̀ wu ̀ ɓsiyɛn ɓi mɛ ̀ nig mɛ mɛ ri mɛ ̀ tɛnɛn .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , di Abiraham a ̀ ka yin , mɛ ̀ m ̀ ɓagha ̀ .
Ti ̀ tanɛɛ yi ̀ lɔŋ naa ̀ -za ̀ y n ̀ ɗogakɛn lɛ gba ̀ g-gba ̀ a ̀ g . Ɓɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ naa ̀ -za ̀ y ɓɛ ̀ rɛrɛliyɛn lɔŋ a mɛ ̀ suunaa wɔ ̀ lɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ŋwa ̀ ri mɛ ̀ suunaa , tyɛ ̀ ki tanɛn mum ɓi ɗu ̀ m nsoo ̀ bog .
Ɓaa ri ̀ lɛ ɓɛ kaɓ ti ̀ ra ̀ a ̀ re ti ̀ n dune n ̀ kɛŋɛn lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ɓɛ fa mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni mɛ mii ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sogha ̀ sogha .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ri ̀ kpaa ɗin ̀ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ lɔŋ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n lɛ : Kɔ ̀ ɔ risi , ɓaya lɔŋ ri ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n .
A ̀ a lɔŋ foo ri foo , ti nya ̀ anyaa ̀ rɛ ̀ n girig ri ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mis , lɛ ti ̀ yii lɛ n ̀ tɔɓ wu ti wu kila ̀ g lɛ mum a ɓa ri ̀ ki ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ri ̀ ,
Ɓisuu kiɓan kin ̀ nnɛ n ̀ ɗomga ̀ y mi ̀ ni Timote a ́ man wɛm ̀ a ̀ n ̀ ɗem a ̀ nɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi ri nyi ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ; nnyɛɛ ri mi ̀ ni bii ̀ yitii ɓiɓan ɓi mɛ ̀ ɛ nnɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ ɓi cɛɓ kɛ ̀ m ki ɓi Kiris , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi nki re ̀ resi ja ̀ ŋ bimiɗ ɓi ɓi ̀ seŋi ɓi Kiris ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Syeesyee a ̀ mum a ̀ ti a ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi syeesyee lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ n ̀ ɗem ; ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki mum ki kila ̀ g ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓeɓtɛn lɛ , ki ri ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki n ̀ ɗem , lɛ ŋwɔm wu mum wɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa kiɓan ki ki roni nyi n ̀ ɗem .
