Aristarikɛ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y ri ̀ mɛ ̀ a ̀ to ̀ gsii yi ̀ mi ̀ ni , nsoo ̀ Marikus a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɔn ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas . Marikus a ̀ nɛ ̀ n innɛ ti ̀ mɛ kpaa mini lɛ i a ̀ yu ̀ u foo a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , ɓi ̀ gha ̀ ɓ nyi lɛ syeesyee .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a Sa ̀ ne ̀ di ̀ rɛŋ ɗi ̀ coo ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ ɓi nɗem lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a n ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ , ki ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ kiɓan lɛ , ɓɔɔ ghɛn mɛ ̀ tɔɓ lɛ , ɗii ɗi Yeesus .
Fɔɔnnɛ ti ̀ i n-yɔɔsii jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bog lɛ : Ti ɓɔn ̀ ɓumɓɛ ti ̀ romii ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi Pol ɓɛɛ ̀ Ɓarinaɓas , ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓis ɓɛ n ̀ ɗem .
Mɛɛ mɛce ̀ m mɛ ɓi ɗiŋii wɔɔ , kaliina ɓumɓɛ mii ̀ lɛ : Fyo ̀ oog a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ɓa ɓi mɛɛ mɛ .
Nni giɓ nyimiɗ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓoɓti ̀ gha ̀ mis ɓi nyi , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ri ̀ kpaa ɗi ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ lɛ : Ŋwaa ̀ nɛnii a ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi nɗaŋ wu ɓumɓɛ ̀ n .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ rɛri ̀ gha ̀ , a ̀ kpaa ɓum lɛ : Reŋiinas ̀ mɛ ̀ nyi ; ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ki ̀ regii ɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Te ̀ e ̀ si nyoo u pɛsɛn aɗyoo , nnyɛɛ ̀ regi wɔ .
Ɓi ̀ si ɓɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ghɛɓsii ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛ ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ca ̀ rɛn ɓi-ɓwɛɗ waa ; tyɛ ̀ ki kaa lɛ ti ki ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓyɛɛ puɓsi ɓi ̀ si nɗem .
Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɗigha ̀ ɓɛ wura ̀ g , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tɛka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓɛgha ̀ ɓi ɓi rɔ ̀ ɓta ̀ ka ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɗ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ pisa .
