Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ yiti ̀ ɗi a maa ɓa ri ̀ ɗyɔ fi ̀ ɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɗi ri ; ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi a ̀ roo ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ Kan wi ̀ s .
Ɓa ̀ ghina mɛ ̀ n ̀ tɔɔ ̀ tɔɔgh wu ; Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ mi ̀ ni Nghay wi ̀ i ̀ ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ ɓe ̀ ga ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna gi ̀ n ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ wog , ɓi ̀ ki gherɛn Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ ?
Nni bee inɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ reni ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ a Isirayɛl yɛɛ ̀ nɛ : Kan lɛ : Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ foŋi ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓyɛm ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ maa n ̀ ka ̀ n ɓɔ ɓyɔ ɓi mɛ ̀ rem , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll wa ̀ a ̀ , ɓɔɔ ɓa ɓum ɓɛm .
