Nni gɔ ̀ n i ̀ Eroɗyaadɛ i ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ y ɓi naa i ̀ ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ , i ̀ tum ri ̀ ɗyen . I ̀ rɔɔ lɛ ri ̀ Eroodɛ , ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ a ki ̀ sɛ ̀ nɛ ̀ . Ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi ̀ kali min ŋwutya ̀ a ̀ gɔ ̀ n a ̀ nɛn lɛ : Tɔgha ̀ mɛ ̀ com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki u ̀ kɔ ̀ ni n ̀ fa wɔ ̀ kɔ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɗiɗi ̀ gha ̀ , nni Yeesus a ̀ teka ̀ bi ̀ rɛs , a ̀ fa Bɛ ̀ ll ɓi ̀ to ̀ gsɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ɓɛg min yɔ ̀ , a ̀ fa ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Terina , nyoo yɛ ̀ m yɛ ̀ ɛ ri lɛ ̀ .
Lɛ di mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓasɛn jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ bog lɛ ɓi kemzi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ Seŋi Kan wi ̀ s Yeesus Kiris .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ yigha ̀ ɓi nɗem wii lɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛɛ ̀ ŋwɔ ̀ ŋwɔŋi nyi ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ , nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki kɛɓtii mi ̀ ni fi ̀ ɓa ̀ g ?
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kaa gɛ bee inɛ lɛ a ghɛɓsi cɛɓ kii , a ̀ ɗimzii gɛ kɔ . Fɔɔnnɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɗimzii gɛ cɛɓ kii nnyɛɛ ki ɓatii gɛ ri ̀ kɔ .
Ghɛn yɛɛ ri min lɛ a ̀ tɔɓ mi ̀ ni di ɓi ̀ falɛɛ ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi kirɔɔ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ?
Nni mɛ ̀ nig mɛ coo don inɛ i ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ̀ nga ̀ mɛɛ ki yogsi ̀ gha ̀ ti ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ɗyoo ri ̀ zi ɓi ɓi ɓagha ̀ n ̀ tonto .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ teka ̀ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni , ɓɛ ki lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ reɓka ̀ ka ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ki ; fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɔlɛ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ sa ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n a ̀ kpaŋ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɓanga ̀ nyi ɓi ca ̀ g , a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ nyi aɗyoo , ŋwutya ̀ a ̀ ki rɛli mɛrɛ ̀ y .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛ ̀ nga ̀ ŋwos adɛŋ ɓi ja ̀ ŋ i bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , nni ti ̀ tulɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ gɔ ̀ n i ̀ giɓ idɛŋ i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓii ̀ sasali ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ; i ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay , ki ki fafa ̀ gha ̀ yɔ ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ , yɛ ̀ ɛ log ki ̀ yii ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi ri ɓii ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ masa ̀ ɓii ɓɛ fɔ ̀ nfɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi ɓi ̀ fyeŋ ɓii ɓin ̀ .
ki ̀ ɓan kifog jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ . Jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛn i ̀ ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ wogsi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Ɓya ̀ a woogh fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ma ̀ a kpaa mi ̀ ni lɛ n ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ , m ̀ ɓii ̀ ki sugtii yi a lɔ ̀ ŋkin . I ɓya ̀ a keesii mɛ ̀ di ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ rɛ ̀ n lɛ , n ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta ɓisuulɛ , Ta ̀ a ̀ ta a ̀ ceetii mɛ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ regi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : N ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni ɓi saaɗ lɛ , ri ̀ fa ɗi maa n ̀ kpɔɓ a giɓ anɛ ɗi cee ri mum bimiɗ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ pii ̀ gh mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni ɓi fi ̀ kɔrɔŋ ;
Nni Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghe ̀ mzi ̀ gha ̀ Kan a ɓi ̀ loŋ , a ̀ ghe ̀ mzii gɛ girig ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wii .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki riɗi ki kpaga ̀ , nni Yeesus a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi zi nɗaŋ ri ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗi .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ ɓi ̀ dɛ ̀ ndɛm ɓi Pol ɓin ̀ , nnɛ ti ̀ gha ̀ ska ̀ ki ̀ kaa ̀ bee i ̀ nɛ lɛ ti kɛn ̀ a Masedwan , lɛ ti ̀ kona ̀ ka ̀ ki ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ regii ɓi ̀ si lɛ , ti kɛn ̀ ki ̀ kalii Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ wɔɔ .
