Ɓisuulɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ɓyom innɛ ɓɛ ɓii ̀ fatii lɛ a ̀ ɓa ri ̀ ɓyɔ lɛɛ ̀ gwey , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ com , ɓɛ ɓatɛ ̀ n maa ga ̀ ɓ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ nyi .
